name: 美少女万華鏡－理と迷宮の少女－蓮華 / Bishojo Mangekyo－Kotowari to Meikyu no Shojo－ Renge / 美少女万华镜－理与迷宫的少女－ 莲华
description:
2023,04,23 v3.1

提升了一点泛用性，其余的和下面一样。

Google Translate:

A little generality has been improved, and the rest is the same as below.

2023,04,20 v3.0

三个衣服能正常画出来了，和服最容易(素材给多了)，另外两个难

和服：Renge-ki, kimono

私服：Renge-pc, black dress

水手服：Renge-se, serafuku

这三个衣服nsfw有点费劲，低强度描述一下人物在画。

（模型练的很强，建议小于0.5）

Google Translate:

The three clothes can be drawn normally, The kimono is the easiest (more materials are given), the other two are difficult.

Kimono: Renge-ki, kimono

Private Clothes: Renge-pc, black dress

serafuku: Renge-se, serafuku

The nsfw of these three clothes is a bit difficult, the intensity is low, describe the characters again, and then go to draw.

(The model is very strong, it is recommended to be less than 0.5)

OLD

v1.0 更像 不好换衣服，v2.0不像 更好换衣服， 强度0.6-0.8，例图用的 Cetus-Mix V3

两件衣服：kimono, dress

Google Translate:

v1.0 is more similar, but it is not easy to change clothes, v2.0 is easy to change clothes, and the strength is controlled at 0.6-0.8, the example picture is used Cetus-Mix V3

two clothes: kimono, dress
